Interface IProposition

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<IProposition>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Proposition
public interface IProposition
extends java.lang.Comparable<IProposition>

A proposal that Ernest enacts a schema. A proposal consists of the proposed schema and a weight that determines the strength of the proposal. Schemas that receive the highest summarized proposal weight are selected for enaction.

Author:
mcohen, ogeorgeon
